## Performance Optimization Tips

### For Development Machine
```
1. Close unnecessary applications
2. Allocate more RAM to Android Studio:
   Help → Edit Custom Properties
   Add: -Xmx4096m
3. Use SSD for faster builds
4. Enable "Instant Run" in Run menu
```

### For Emulator
```
1. Use latest system image
2. Allocate sufficient RAM (2-4GB)
3. Use x86_64 architecture
4. Enable "Use Host GPU" in emulator settings
```

### For App
```
1. Use ProGuard for release builds
2. Optimize images and assets
3. Use ViewBinding instead of findViewById
4. Implement proper caching strategies
```

