## Useful Commands

```bash
# Clean build
./gradlew clean

# Build debug APK
./gradlew assembleDebug

# Build release APK
./gradlew assembleRelease

# Run unit tests
./gradlew test

# Run instrumented tests
./gradlew connectedAndroidTest

# Check dependencies
./gradlew dependencies

# Update dependencies
./gradlew dependencyUpdates

# Enable verbose logging
./gradlew build --stacktrace --debug

# List tasks
./gradlew tasks
```

